### 🧪 VoM API - Direct Testing (Without Our Backend)
### اختبار VoM API مباشرة (بدون Backend)

@vomBaseUrl = https://kimoo.getvom.com
@email = Info@aleairygroup.com
@password = Aa1xyjPlNHd

### ========================================
### 1️⃣ Step 1: Login to VoM API (Get Token)
### الخطوة 1: تسجيل الدخول للحصول على Token
POST {{vomBaseUrl}}/api/companyuser/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Api-Agent: zapier
Accept-Language: en

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### ========================================
### 2️⃣ Step 2: Get Accounts (Replace TOKEN with token from Step 1)
### الخطوة 2: جلب الحسابات (استبدل TOKEN بالرمز من الخطوة 1)
GET {{vomBaseUrl}}/api/accounting/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Api-Agent: zapier
Accept-Language: en
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### 3️⃣ Get Accounts (Arabic)
### جلب الحسابات (عربي)
GET {{vomBaseUrl}}/api/accounting/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Api-Agent: zapier
Accept-Language: ar
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### 4️⃣ Test with cURL (Copy and paste in terminal)
### اختبار باستخدام cURL
### First: Login
# curl -X POST "https://kimoo.getvom.com/api/companyuser/login" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -H "Accept: application/json" \
#   -H "Api-Agent: zapier" \
#   -H "Accept-Language: en" \
#   -d "{\"email\":\"Info@aleairygroup.com\",\"password\":\"Aa1xyjPlNHd\"}"

### Then: Get Accounts (replace TOKEN with actual token)
# curl -X GET "https://kimoo.getvom.com/api/accounting/accounts?language=en" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -H "Accept: application/json" \
#   -H "Api-Agent: zapier" \
#   -H "Accept-Language: en" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE"
